# EF Core migrations (optional snapshots)
ChoirAdminApp/Migrations/*Designer.cs
ChoirAdminApp/Migrations/*Snapshot.cs

# Test & coverage
ChoirAdminApp/TestResults/
ChoirAdminApp/coverage/